productData.body_html:

The Spike Jacket by Handstich is an ideal layering piece for springtime breezes. Resistant against wind and rain, this piece is a classic comfort. Stand up collar with adjustable, hidden hood with zip closure. Elastic drawstring at waist, elastic cuffs. Mesh shoulder panels. Three front zip pockets at front, one interior pocket. Zip closure at center front. Color Dark Olive. 100% Nylon, Lining 100% Polyester. Addis is wearing a Size 48.
